                <mxCell id="80" value="1.&amp;nbsp; In both the cases, static and non-static property, and whether&amp;nbsp; property is public or private,&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;A static method can access static variables and method only but Instance method can access both class and instance variable and methods&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" vertex="1" parent="79">
