                <mxCell id="74" value="&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; position: relative; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe WPC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, system-ui, Ubuntu, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-wrap-mode: wrap;&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;code-line&quot; data-line=&quot;69&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;position: relative;&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;code-line&quot; data-line=&quot;69&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Static → Static:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Static methods can access static variables, One copy shared by all instances ✓&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;position: relative;&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;code-line&quot; data-line=&quot;70&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instance → Instance:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Instance methods can access instance variables. Each instance has its own copy ✓&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;position: relative;&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;code-line&quot; data-line=&quot;71&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instance → Static:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Instance methods can access static variables ✓&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;position: relative;&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;code-line&quot; data-line=&quot;72&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Class → Static:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Accessing static through class name ✓&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;position: relative;&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;code-line&quot; data-line=&quot;73&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instance → Static:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Accessing static through instance ✓ (but not recommended)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;" vertex="1" parent="1">
